job.title: FACT Technician Recruitment 2021  Apply offline for Various Vacancies in Kerala
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Engineer Graduate Apprentice

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by Fertilizers and Chemicals Travancore Limited for the vacancies of Engineer Graduate Apprentice. If you are finding a government job in Kerala then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Kerala, from 18.05.2021, and till 28.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Kerala and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Offline
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for FACT Engineer Graduate Apprentice vacancies in Kerala:

  • To apply for an Engineer Graduate Apprentice posts in Kerala, your ITI, Degree must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these vacancies is the 18.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these vacancies is 28.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 35  years old. 

FACT Engineer Graduate Apprentice Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 25,000

How to apply for FACT Technician Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly download the application form there and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Kerala. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of FACT and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY FACT.
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the detailed ask in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned in the official notification

Download Official notification pdf
